  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Genjutsu (Compulsion)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 12</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 15</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 29 | <b>Successes:</b> 8</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 17 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 37</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H, Mas</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You speak in a clear voice, giving the target an order that it can understand (if no common language exists, you can only convey basic instructions such as 'go there' or 'fight that person'). The subject obeys the order, and prioritizes it above all other things, completing it to the best of its ability. Other creatures can determine that its actions are being influenced with a Sense Motive check (DC 15).<br><br>An obviously self-destructive order will not be carried out, and each time you target the same creature within a 24 hour period beyond the first time, it gains a +2 cumulative bonus to its Will save to resist it. The technique automatically ends if the instructions given have been completed.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
